rows.name: Ask Reggie about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0001
rows.name:
Recently, I happened to destroy the stomach of a
tectinsula in Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0002
rows.name:
Some very rare materials fell out of it,
including orange tequila and topaz wine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Those liquids must have originally been used by the
tectinsula as digestive juices.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0004
rows.name:
It seems that a powerful shock to the abdomen
causes a crystallizing chemical reaction that turns
them into gem-like materials.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0005
rows.name:
If you happen across any tectinsulas yourself,
you should make a point to destroy their abdomens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0008
rows.name:
Clarissa and I had talked about it a lot—she said that
as Bozé's last remaining students, we should always be
proud and act with courage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0009
rows.name: So I'm not going to cry or be afraid anymore.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0010
rows.name:
Clarissa never gave in even at the very end,
and I want to fight in a way that makes her proud.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0011
rows.name:
And I also want to help find the Lifehold Core so we
can bring her back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0019
rows.name:
Have you heard of dangerous indigens called duoguills
that emit electric shocks?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0020
rows.name:
Bozé promised me that something good would happen
if I destroyed their tentacles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0021
rows.name:
After I destroyed one with a focused attack,
I was able to pick it up and sell it for a lot of money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0022
rows.name:
Apparently their tentacles are salvageable materials that
can be used for weapon production and other stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0023
rows.name:
It's just like Bozé to know something like that.
I'm so glad that I decided to go along with him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0026
rows.name:
A little while ago, we managed to ambush a squad of
Prone and kill them all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0027
rows.name:
Ha ha! I'll never forget the look of fear on their
faces when we leapt from the shadows![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0028
rows.name:
I know that won't make up for what they did to
Clarissa and the others...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0029
rows.name:
But Bozé and I are going to keep battling against the
xenoforms. We won't ever forget what they did![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0031
rows.name:
That's the spirit, Reggie! Whatever troubles block your
path, you must clear them without fear or hesitation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0032
rows.name:
Don't shirk your responsibility to the others.
Hold their thoughts close, and never let the xenos win![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0049
rows.name:
This Ma-non named Jejebba has been helping me out
with my missions lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0050
rows.name:
On one recent mission, he used this weird radar
device to find some stranded companions of mine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0051
rows.name:
I guess there really are all kinds of xenoforms.
Though I can't forgive the ones that killed Clarissa.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0052
rows.name:
Still, I'm going to stop resenting alien races just
because they're different from us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0053
rows.name:
Could this be some of that "enlightenment" stuff that
Bozé is always talking about?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0055
rows.name: You finally begin to understand. Well done, son.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0056
rows.name:
The way of the Buddha is seeing the soul within instead
of the form without.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0060
rows.name: BLADE used to be full of Bozé's disciples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0061
rows.name:
They were exceptional people who bravely challenged
some of the most difficult missions BLADE had to offer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0062
rows.name:
And that's why so many of them have...lost their lives.
In fact, I believe there's only one other BLADE in active
duty besides myself who studied under Bozé.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016401_MSG0063
rows.name: So I can understand why he treats us like family.[ST:wait ]
